{"tid":2142634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］根正苗紅  正統中文教學","createTime":"2020-08-06T14:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:02:56.000Z","uid":359260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f939b4722ddcc3b9cd49352117004c48a07b169","tid":2142634,"uid":359260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學好中文 人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小香港：臨時醫院<br />\n大陸：方艙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：化驗<br />\n大陸：檢測<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：DNA、基因<br />\n大陸：核酸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：停頓、癱瘓<br />\n大陸：停擺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：建造、建設、營造<br />\n大陸：打造<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：第三輪、第三次、第三度爆發<br />\n大陸：第三波爆發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小香港：把握時間、從速、加快<br />\n大陸：抓緊時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img